":"正常條款銀行係可以隨時要你還晒。<br />\n唔理你幾掂。<br />\n但整臭名既野唔做姐。"},{"pid":"e05b048ccd8f50c88c781a9b1f5620283021891c","tid":142144,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T01:33:27.000Z","msg":"失業咗年半都冇call 我 loan <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ad59b9a6df04fa5b1cf9ab254fc8aa2fcde4b4a","tid":142144,"uid":66157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T01:40:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>失業咗年半都冇call 我 loan <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你話冇供年半就call loan，你月月供，你有錢還佢理得你乞食咩"},{"pid":"0da1a9e9a6e864b1c3474a4311994d8e58c94deb","tid":142144,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T01:46:45.000Z","msg":"我睇過關於房地產法入面關於mortgage<br />\n我記憶中你準時還錢佢係無權call loan"},{"pid":"a72d1147bc14fc03717d147b832bdf3186746a57","tid":142144,"uid":2114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T02:33:55.000Z","msg":"會<br />\n<br />\n建議擔心嘅人<br />\n買樓一定要full pay"},{"pid":"93e2911882e8f3c8aac95ab023fd67a6e6f17b23","tid":142144,"uid":16112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T03:35:01.000Z","msg":"唔好講買樓，就算你問銀行私人貸款，信用卡，你簽個份文件都有一項話銀行有權要求你即時還哂所以錢。<br />\n<br />\n只不過好多人覺得銀行唔會咁做，所以唔理。<br />\n其實好on9，知道有個case係銀行call loan，個事主話銀行做法不妥，但係佢自己簽份野寫到明銀行有權咁做而佢同意，咁銀行call loan有什麼問題？佢話佢簽個陣以為人地講下，冇可能會做。"},{"pid":"5110804bd7fe350f58e358f6602d938f9f372fd4","tid":142144,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T03:50:50.000Z","msg":"一下子要人還曬，大把人要破產，到時銀行d壞賬多多幾百倍，你話銀行想唔想見到咁呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e6aac14e14cfa536efbae537fabefb87df90f1b","tid":142144,"uid":36390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T05:03:38.000Z","msg":"銀行絕對有權call loan，按揭係貸款嚟"},{"pid":"bb2130a314f1066fa8535bacbee24a14ebc08306","tid":142144,"uid":54986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T05